damn thing off. Please.

247
00:18:55.635 --> 00:18:58.036
Of course. Heh. you're sloshed.

248
00:18:58.270 --> 00:19:02.537
Oh. yes. Yes. I am sloshed.

249
00:19:02.775 --> 00:19:03.936
